<html>

<head>
	<title>The Blockchain University</title>
</head>

<body>
<div style="font-family: Helvetica; padding: 9%; background-color: #ffffff; color: #333333; font-size: 17px;">
	<!-- Header -->
	<div style="vertical-align: middle; ">
		<img src="https://theblockchainu.com/assets/images/bu_logo.png" width="auto" height="35px" >  <span style="position: relative; top: -14px; color: #ff5b5f"></span>
	</div>
	<!-- Title -->
	<div style="font-weight: 800; font-size: 30px; margin-top: 40px;">
		Your session request was rejected
	</div>
	<!-- Body -->
	<div>
		<div style="font-size: 17px; margin-top: 25px;">
			Hey there,
		</div>
		<div style="font-size: 17px; margin-top: 10px; line-height: 24px">
			<%= teacherName%> has rejected your request to start a new peer session with them.
			<br><br>
			The request was for session dated <%= formattedDate %> from <%= startTime%> to <%= endTime%>.
			<br><br>
			While rejecting legitimate session requests is highly condemned on The Blockchain University, teachers sometimes do cancel requests based on their review of your profile. You can get in touch with the teacher to know more.
		</div>
		<div style="font-size: 21px; margin-top: 40px; line-height: 24px; background-color: #ff5b5f; color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 4px;">
			<a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://theblockchainu.com/console/learning/sessions">View my request</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<!-- Signature -->
	<div style="font-size: 17px; margin-top: 30px; line-height: 24px;">
		Cheers,
		<br>
		The Blockchain U Team
	</div>
	<!-- Footer -->
	<hr style="margin-top: 40px; background-color: #dbdbdb;">
	<div style="font-size: 13px; color: #bbbbbb; margin-top: 30px; font-weight: 300">
		Sent with <span style="font-size: 11px;">&hearts;</span> from The Blockchain U
		<br><br>
		Peerbuds, Inc., 4580 Automall Pkwy, Fremont, CA 94538
	</div>
</div>
</body>

</html>